// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
// CONFIG: Validate inputs and setup monitoring parameters
// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê

const input = $input.first().json;

// Check if triggered by webhook or manual
const isManual = !input.user_email;

const config = {
  user_email: input.user_email || "user@example.com",  // ‚ö†Ô∏è REPLACE if running manually
  api_key: input.api_key || "YOUR_API_KEY",  // ‚ö†Ô∏è REPLACE if running manually
  buyer_wallet: input.buyer_wallet || "YOUR_WALLET_ADDRESS",  // ‚ö†Ô∏è REPLACE with your wallet (0x...)
  tx_hash: input.tx_hash || null,
  trigger_source: input.trigger_source || "manual",

  // Monitoring settings
  time_range_hours: 24,
  payment_history_limit: 50,  // Fetch last 50 for display (use curl for full history)
  audit_log_limit: 50,
  export_format: "csv",

  // AgentGatePay API
  api_url: "https://api.agentgatepay.com",
  mcp_endpoint: "https://mcp.agentgatepay.com",

  // Session tracking
  session: {
    id: `monitor_${Date.now()}`,
    started_at: new Date().toISOString(),
    is_manual: isManual
  }
};

// Validation
if (config.api_key === "YOUR_API_KEY") {
  throw new Error("‚ùå Please configure your API key in Node 2 'Load Config'!");
}

console.log(`üìä Monitoring Dashboard Started`);
console.log(`   User: ${config.user_email}`);
console.log(`   Source: ${config.trigger_source}`);
console.log(`   TX Hash: ${config.tx_hash || 'N/A'}`);

return [{ json: { config } }];

// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
// VERIFICATION: Verify last payment on blockchain
// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê

const config = $('2Ô∏è‚É£ Load Config').first().json.config;
const tx_hash = config.tx_hash;

if (!tx_hash) {
  console.log('‚ö†Ô∏è  No tx_hash provided - skipping verification');
  return [{ json: { 
    verified: false, 
    reason: "No transaction hash provided",
    config: config
  }}];
}

console.log(`üîç Verifying payment: ${tx_hash}`);

return [{ json: { 
  tx_hash: tx_hash,
  config: config,
  should_verify: true
}}];

return [{ json: { 
  verified: false,
  reason: "No transaction to verify",
  message: "Skipped verification - no tx_hash provided"
}}];

// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
// STATISTICS: Calculate spending trends and alerts
// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê

const config = $('2Ô∏è‚É£ Load Config').first().json.config;
const analytics = $('3Ô∏è‚É£ üìà Get User Analytics').first().json;
const payment_history_response = $('4Ô∏è‚É£ üí≥ Get Payment History').first().json;
const audit_logs_response = $('5Ô∏è‚É£ üìã Get Audit Logs (24h)').first().json;
const mandates_response = $('6Ô∏è‚É£ üîë Get Active Mandates').first().json;
const verification = $input.first().json;

console.log('üìä Calculating statistics...');

// Parse payment history (MCP response)
let payments = [];
if (payment_history_response.result && payment_history_response.result.content) {
  try {
    const content = payment_history_response.result.content[0].text;
    const parsed = JSON.parse(content);
    payments = parsed.payments || [];
  } catch (e) {
    console.log('‚ö†Ô∏è  Could not parse payment history');
  }
}

// Parse audit logs
const logs = audit_logs_response.logs || [];

// Parse mandates
const mandates = mandates_response.logs || [];

// ‚úÖ FIX: Use correct API field names and calculate average AFTER getting values
// API returns: total_spent_usd, transaction_count (NOT payment_count)
const total_spent = analytics.total_spent_usd || 0;
const payment_count = analytics.transaction_count || 0;  // ‚úÖ FIXED: was analytics.payment_count
const average_payment = payment_count > 0 ? (total_spent / payment_count) : 0;  // ‚úÖ Calculate after

const stats = {
  // Spending stats - FIXED field names to match API response
  total_spent: total_spent,
  payment_count: payment_count,
  average_payment: average_payment,

  // Recent activity
  payments_last_24h: payments.filter(p => {
    const paymentTime = new Date(p.timestamp || p.created_at);
    const oneDayAgo = new Date(Date.now() - 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000);
    return paymentTime > oneDayAgo;
  }).length,

  spent_last_24h: payments.filter(p => {
    const paymentTime = new Date(p.timestamp || p.created_at);
    const oneDayAgo = new Date(Date.now() - 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000);
    return paymentTime > oneDayAgo;
  }).reduce((sum, p) => sum + parseFloat(p.amount_usd || 0), 0),

  // Mandate stats
  active_mandates: mandates.filter(m => {
    const details = typeof m.details === 'string' ? JSON.parse(m.details) : m.details;
    return details.status === 'active' || details.status === 'issued';
  }).length,

  total_budget: mandates.reduce((sum, m) => {
    const details = typeof m.details === 'string' ? JSON.parse(m.details) : m.details;
    return sum + parseFloat(details.budget_usd || 0);
  }, 0),

  budget_remaining: mandates.reduce((sum, m) => {
    const details = typeof m.details === 'string' ? JSON.parse(m.details) : m.details;
    return sum + parseFloat(details.budget_remaining || 0);
  }, 0),

  // Audit log stats
  total_events_24h: logs.length,
  payment_events: logs.filter(l => l.event_type && l.event_type.includes('payment')).length,
  mandate_events: logs.filter(l => l.event_type && l.event_type.includes('mandate')).length,
  aif_events: logs.filter(l => l.event_type && l.event_type.includes('aif')).length,

  // Most recent payment
  last_payment: payments.length > 0 ? payments[0] : null,

  // Verification status
  last_payment_verified: verification.verified || false
};

// Calculate budget utilization
stats.budget_utilization_pct = stats.total_budget > 0
  ? ((stats.total_budget - stats.budget_remaining) / stats.total_budget * 100).toFixed(2)
  : 0;

// Spending trend (compare last 24h to average)
stats.spending_trend = stats.payment_count > 0
  ? (stats.spent_last_24h > stats.average_payment ? 'increasing' : 'stable')
  : 'no_activity';

console.log(`   Total Spent: $${stats.total_spent}`);
console.log(`   Payments (24h): ${stats.payments_last_24h}`);
console.log(`   Budget Remaining: $${stats.budget_remaining}`);
console.log(`   Budget Utilization: ${stats.budget_utilization_pct}%`);

return [{ json: { config, analytics, stats, payments, logs, mandates, verification } }];

// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
// ALERTS: Check for warnings and important notifications
// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê

const data = $input.first().json;
const { stats, mandates, payments } = data;

const alerts = [];

// Alert 1: Low budget warning
if (stats.budget_remaining > 0 && stats.budget_utilization_pct > 90) {
  alerts.push({
    severity: 'high',
    type: 'budget_low',
    message: `‚ö†Ô∏è  BUDGET WARNING: Only $${stats.budget_remaining.toFixed(2)} remaining (${stats.budget_utilization_pct}% used)`,
    action: 'Issue new mandate or reduce spending'
  });
} else if (stats.budget_remaining > 0 && stats.budget_utilization_pct > 75) {
  alerts.push({
    severity: 'medium',
    type: 'budget_warning',
    message: `‚ÑπÔ∏è  Budget Notice: $${stats.budget_remaining.toFixed(2)} remaining (${stats.budget_utilization_pct}% used)`,
    action: 'Monitor spending'
  });
}

// Alert 2: Mandate expiration warning
mandates.forEach(m => {
  const details = typeof m.details === 'string' ? JSON.parse(m.details) : m.details;
  if (details.ttl_remaining_hours && details.ttl_remaining_hours < 24) {
    alerts.push({
      severity: 'high',
      type: 'mandate_expiring',
      message: `‚è∞ MANDATE EXPIRING: ${details.mandate_id} expires in ${details.ttl_remaining_hours} hours`,
      action: 'Renew mandate before expiration'
    });
  }
});

// Alert 3: No recent activity
if (stats.payments_last_24h === 0 && stats.payment_count > 0) {
  alerts.push({
    severity: 'low',
    type: 'no_activity',
    message: '‚ÑπÔ∏è  No payments in last 24 hours',
    action: 'Normal - no action needed'
  });
}

// Alert 4: Failed payments
const failed_payments = payments.filter(p => p.status === 'failed');
if (failed_payments.length > 0) {
  alerts.push({
    severity: 'high',
    type: 'payment_failures',
    message: `‚ùå FAILED PAYMENTS: ${failed_payments.length} payment(s) failed`,
    action: 'Review failed transactions',
    failed_txs: failed_payments.map(p => p.tx_hash)
  });
}

// Alert 5: High spending rate
if (stats.spent_last_24h > stats.average_payment * 10 && stats.payment_count > 10) {
  alerts.push({
    severity: 'medium',
    type: 'high_spending',
    message: `üìà High Spending: $${stats.spent_last_24h.toFixed(2)} spent in 24h (10x average)`,
    action: 'Verify spending is intentional'
  });
}

// Alert 6: Verification failure
if (data.verification && !data.verification.verified && data.config.tx_hash) {
  alerts.push({
    severity: 'medium',
    type: 'verification_failed',
    message: `‚ö†Ô∏è  Payment verification issue: ${data.verification.reason || 'Unknown'}`,
    action: 'Check transaction on blockchain explorer'
  });
}

console.log(`üö® Alerts: ${alerts.length} alert(s)`);
alerts.forEach((a, i) => {
  console.log(`   ${i+1}. [${a.severity.toUpperCase()}] ${a.message}`);
});

return [{ json: { ...data, alerts } }];

// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
// DASHBOARD DATA: Format metrics for hybrid display
// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê

const data = $input.first().json;
const { config, analytics, stats, alerts } = data;

// Create dashboard-ready data structure
const dashboard = {
  // Header
  title: "üìä Buyer Monitoring Dashboard",
  user: config.user_email,
  generated_at: new Date().toISOString(),
  session_id: config.session.id,

  // Key metrics (shown in N8N)
  metrics: {
    total_spent: {
      value: `$${stats.total_spent.toFixed(2)}`,
      label: "Total Spent",
      icon: "üí∞"
    },
    payment_count: {
      value: stats.payment_count,
      label: "Total Payments",
      icon: "üí≥"
    },
    budget_remaining: {
      value: `$${stats.budget_remaining.toFixed(2)}`,
      label: "Budget Remaining",
      icon: "üîë",
      percentage: `${stats.budget_utilization_pct}% used`
    },
    active_mandates: {
      value: stats.active_mandates,
      label: "Active Mandates",
      icon: "üé´"
    },
    payments_24h: {
      value: stats.payments_last_24h,
      label: "Payments (24h)",
      icon: "üìà",
      amount: `$${stats.spent_last_24h.toFixed(2)}`
    },
    events_24h: {
      value: stats.total_events_24h,
      label: "Events Logged (24h)",
      icon: "üìã"
    }
  },

  // Alerts summary
  alerts_summary: {
    count: alerts.length,
    high: alerts.filter(a => a.severity === 'high').length,
    medium: alerts.filter(a => a.severity === 'medium').length,
    low: alerts.filter(a => a.severity === 'low').length,
    items: alerts
  },

  // Quick stats
  quick_stats: {
    average_payment: `$${stats.average_payment.toFixed(2)}`,
    spending_trend: stats.spending_trend,
    budget_utilization: `${stats.budget_utilization_pct}%`,
    last_payment_verified: stats.last_payment_verified ? '‚úÖ Verified' : '‚è≥ Pending'
  },

  // Links
  links: {
    user_analytics: `${config.api_url}/v1/analytics/me`,
    audit_logs: `${config.api_url}/audit/logs?client_id=${config.user_email}`,
    payment_history: `${config.api_url}/v1/payments/list`
  },

  // Export options
  export: {
    csv_available: true,
    json_available: true,
    pdf_available: false
  }
};

console.log('üìä Dashboard data prepared');
console.log(`   Metrics: ${Object.keys(dashboard.metrics).length}`);
console.log(`   Alerts: ${dashboard.alerts_summary.count}`);

return [{ json: { ...data, dashboard } }];

// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
// CSV EXPORT: Generate downloadable CSV report
// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê

const data = $input.first().json;
const { config, stats, payments, logs, mandates, alerts } = data;

// CSV Header
let csv = "AgentGatePay Buyer Monitoring Report\n";
csv += `Generated: ${new Date().toISOString()}\n`;
csv += `User: ${config.user_email}\n`;
csv += `\n`;

// Summary section
csv += "SUMMARY\n";
csv += "Metric,Value\n";
csv += `Total Spent,$${stats.total_spent}\n`;
csv += `Payment Count,${stats.payment_count}\n`;
csv += `Average Payment,$${stats.average_payment}\n`;
csv += `Budget Remaining,$${stats.budget_remaining}\n`;
csv += `Budget Utilization,${stats.budget_utilization_pct}%\n`;
csv += `Active Mandates,${stats.active_mandates}\n`;
csv += `Payments (24h),${stats.payments_last_24h}\n`;
csv += `Spent (24h),$${stats.spent_last_24h}\n`;
csv += `\n`;

// Alerts section
if (alerts.length > 0) {
  csv += "ALERTS\n";
  csv += "Severity,Type,Message,Action\n";
  alerts.forEach(a => {
    csv += `${a.severity},${a.type},"${a.message}","${a.action}"\n`;
  });
  csv += `\n`;
}

// Payment history - MERCHANT PAYMENTS
csv += "MERCHANT PAYMENTS (Last 20)\n";
csv += "Timestamp,TX Hash,Amount USD,Status,Merchant Address\n";
const merchant_logs = logs.filter(log => log.event_type === 'x402_payment_settled');
merchant_logs.slice(0, 20).forEach(log => {
  const details = log.details;
  csv += `${new Date(details.timestamp * 1000).toISOString()},${details.tx_hash},$${details.amount_usd},${details.status || 'completed'},${details.receiver_address}\n`;
});
csv += `\n`;

// COMMISSION PAYMENTS
csv += "COMMISSION PAYMENTS (Last 20)\n";
csv += "Timestamp,TX Hash,Amount USD,Status,Gateway Address\n";
const commission_logs = logs.filter(log => log.event_type === 'x402_payment_settled' && log.details.commission_tx_hash);
commission_logs.slice(0, 20).forEach(log => {
  const details = log.details;
  csv += `${new Date(details.timestamp * 1000).toISOString()},${details.commission_tx_hash},$${details.commission_amount_usd || 0},${details.status || 'completed'},${details.commission_address}\n`;
});
csv += `\n`;

// Mandate summary
if (mandates.length > 0) {
  csv += "ACTIVE MANDATES\n";
  csv += "Mandate ID,Budget USD,Remaining USD,TTL Hours,Status\n";
  mandates.forEach(m => {
    const details = typeof m.details === 'string' ? JSON.parse(m.details) : m.details;
    csv += `${details.mandate_id || 'N/A'},$${details.budget_usd || 0},$${details.budget_remaining || 0},${details.ttl_remaining_hours || 'N/A'},${details.status || 'N/A'}\n`;
  });
  csv += `\n`;
}

// Event summary
csv += "EVENT SUMMARY (24h)\n";
csv += "Category,Count\n";
csv += `Total Events,${stats.total_events_24h}\n`;
csv += `Payment Events,${stats.payment_events}\n`;
csv += `Mandate Events,${stats.mandate_events}\n`;
csv += `AIF Security Events,${stats.aif_events}\n`;

console.log('üìÑ CSV export generated');
console.log(`   Size: ${csv.length} characters`);

return [{ json: { ...data, csv_export: csv } }];

