// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
// STATISTICS: Calculate revenue trends and merchant metrics
// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê

const config = $('2Ô∏è‚É£ Load Config1').first().json.config;
const revenue = $('3Ô∏è‚É£ üí∞ Get Merchant Revenue').first().json;
const payments_response = $('4Ô∏è‚É£ üí≥ Get Payment List').first().json;
const webhooks_response = $('5Ô∏è‚É£ üîó Get Webhooks').first().json;
const audit_logs_response = $('6Ô∏è‚É£ üìã Get Audit Logs (24h)').first().json;
const verification = $input.first().json;

console.log('üìä Calculating merchant statistics...');

// Parse payments
const payment_list = payments_response.payments || [];

// Parse webhooks
const webhook_list = webhooks_response.webhooks || [];

// Parse audit logs
const logs = audit_logs_response.logs || [];

// ‚úÖ FIX: Use correct API field names from merchant revenue response
// API returns: total_usd, count, average_usd (NOT total_revenue_usd, payment_count, average_payment_usd)
const total_revenue = revenue.total_usd || 0;
const payment_count = revenue.count || 0;  // ‚úÖ FIXED: use 'count' not 'payment_count'
const average_payment = payment_count > 0 ? (total_revenue / payment_count) : (revenue.average_usd || 0);

const stats = {
  // Revenue stats - FIXED field names to match API response
  total_revenue: total_revenue,
  payment_count: payment_count,
  average_payment: average_payment,
  revenue_this_month: revenue.revenue_this_month || 0,

  // Recent activity
  payments_last_24h: payment_list.filter(p => {
    const paymentTime = new Date(p.timestamp || p.created_at);
    const oneDayAgo = new Date(Date.now() - 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000);
    return paymentTime > oneDayAgo;
  }).length,

  revenue_last_24h: payment_list.filter(p => {
    const paymentTime = new Date(p.timestamp || p.created_at);
    const oneDayAgo = new Date(Date.now() - 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000);
    return paymentTime > oneDayAgo;
  }).reduce((sum, p) => sum + parseFloat(p.amount_usd || 0), 0),

  // Webhook stats
  total_webhooks: webhook_list.length,
  active_webhooks: webhook_list.filter(w => w.status === 'active').length,
  total_deliveries: webhook_list.reduce((sum, w) => sum + (w.delivery_count || 0), 0),
  total_failures: webhook_list.reduce((sum, w) => sum + (w.failure_count || 0), 0),

  // Webhook success rate
  webhook_success_rate: 0,

  // Top buyers
  top_buyers: (revenue.top_buyers || []).slice(0, 5),

  // Audit log stats
  total_events_24h: logs.length,

  // Most recent payment
  last_payment_received: payment_list.length > 0 ? payment_list[0] : null,

  // Verification status
  last_payment_verified: verification.verified || false,

  // Payment success rate
  successful_payments: payment_list.filter(p => p.status === 'completed' || p.status === 'confirmed').length,
  failed_payments: payment_list.filter(p => p.status === 'failed').length
};

// Calculate webhook success rate
const total_webhook_attempts = stats.total_deliveries + stats.total_failures;
stats.webhook_success_rate = total_webhook_attempts > 0
  ? ((stats.total_deliveries / total_webhook_attempts) * 100).toFixed(2)
  : 100;

// Payment success rate
const total_status_known = stats.successful_payments + stats.failed_payments;
stats.payment_success_rate = total_status_known > 0
  ? ((stats.successful_payments / total_status_known) * 100).toFixed(2)
  : 100;

// Revenue growth (compare this month to average)
const months_active = stats.payment_count > 0 ? Math.max(1, stats.payment_count / 30) : 1;
const average_monthly_revenue = stats.total_revenue / months_active;
stats.revenue_growth_pct = average_monthly_revenue > 0
  ? (((stats.revenue_this_month - average_monthly_revenue) / average_monthly_revenue) * 100).toFixed(2)
  : 0;

stats.revenue_trend = parseFloat(stats.revenue_growth_pct) > 0 ? 'growing' : 'stable';

console.log(`   Total Revenue: $${stats.total_revenue}`);
console.log(`   Payments (24h): ${stats.payments_last_24h}`);
console.log(`   Webhooks: ${stats.active_webhooks}/${stats.total_webhooks} active`);
console.log(`   Success Rate: ${stats.payment_success_rate}%`);

return [{ json: { config, revenue, stats, payments: payment_list, webhooks: webhook_list, logs, verification } }];

// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
// ALERTS: Check for merchant warnings and notifications
// ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê

const data = $input.first().json;
const { stats, payments, webhooks } = data;

const alerts = [];

// Alert 1: Webhook delivery failures
if (stats.total_webhooks > 0 && parseFloat(stats.webhook_success_rate) < 95) {
  alerts.push({
    severity: 'high',
    type: 'webhook_failures',
    message: `‚ö†Ô∏è  WEBHOOK ISSUES: Success rate ${stats.webhook_success_rate}% (${stats.total_failures} failures)`,
    action: 'Check webhook URLs and test delivery'
  });
}

// Alert 2: No recent payments
if (stats.payments_last_24h === 0 && stats.payment_count > 0) {
  alerts.push({
    severity: 'medium',
    type: 'no_payments',
    message: '‚è∞ No payments received in last 24 hours',
    action: 'Review - may be normal or check if service is accessible'
  });
}

// Alert 3: Failed payments
if (stats.failed_payments > 0) {
  alerts.push({
    severity: 'high',
    type: 'payment_failures',
    message: `‚ùå PAYMENT FAILURES: ${stats.failed_payments} failed payment(s)`,
    action: 'Review failed transactions and notify buyers'
  });
}

// Alert 4: Large payment received
if (stats.last_payment_received && parseFloat(stats.last_payment_received.amount_usd) > stats.average_payment * 10) {
  alerts.push({
    severity: 'low',
    type: 'large_payment',
    message: `üí∞ Large payment received: $${stats.last_payment_received.amount_usd} (10x average)`,
    action: 'Verify payment and deliver service',
    tx_hash: stats.last_payment_received.tx_hash
  });
}

// Alert 5: Revenue spike
if (stats.revenue_last_24h > stats.average_payment * 20 && stats.payment_count > 10) {
  alerts.push({
    severity: 'low',
    type: 'revenue_spike',
    message: `üìà Revenue Spike: $${stats.revenue_last_24h.toFixed(2)} in 24h (20x average)`,
    action: 'High demand detected - ensure service capacity'
  });
}

// Alert 6: No webhooks configured
if (stats.total_webhooks === 0 && stats.payment_count > 5) {
  alerts.push({
    severity: 'medium',
    type: 'no_webhooks',
    message: '‚ÑπÔ∏è  No webhooks configured - missing payment notifications',
    action: 'Configure webhook to receive real-time payment alerts'
  });
}

// Alert 7: Verification failure
if (data.verification && !data.verification.verified && data.config.tx_hash) {
  alerts.push({
    severity: 'medium',
    type: 'verification_failed',
    message: `‚ö†Ô∏è  Payment verification issue: ${data.verification.reason || 'Unknown'}`,
    action: 'Check transaction on blockchain explorer'
  });
}

// Alert 8: Low payment success rate
if (parseFloat(stats.payment_success_rate) < 90 && stats.payment_count > 10) {
  alerts.push({
    severity: 'high',
    type: 'low_success_rate',
